Text: Updated 10.4.10 Nvidia kexts MAY not work on some AMD systems.
do you guys know if there is a 10.4.10 release for sse2?

There is no SSE2 release yet. This update was just released and it's best to start off with SSE3.

When you install automatically, your extensions are backed up at /10410backup in your OSX partition. If you fail to load after reboot because the Nvidia kexts did not work on your discount AMD system, boot with -f (safemode) and recover the kexts.
